      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "The Queen\u0027s Garden",
        "Client": "Precocious Girl",
        "Description": "I aspire to charming conduct\r\nbecoming of a lovely lady.\r\nThat\u0027s why I want to observe\r\nthe graciousness of the queen\r\ninhabiting the Jungle. I\u0027ll observe\r\nfrom the flowers. You\u0027ll protect\r\nme, won\u0027t you?",
        "Target": "Hunt a Rathian",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Le jardin de la reine",
        "Client": "Fille pr\u00E9cautionneuse",
        "Description": "Je souhaite devenir une vraie dame,\r\net je voudrais donc examiner\r\nla reine dragon qui habite\r\ndans la Jungle. Je la regarderai\r\ndepuis les fleurs.\r\nTu me prot\u00E8geras, hein ?",
